						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><em><strong>&quot;We're all a little mad here.&quot;</strong></em></p> </div> <p>A (relatively) short article about perfectionalism, failure and flopping hard.</p> <p>Thank you so much to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6479803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596020169" alt="HarryBlank" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6479803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" >HarryBlank</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/riemann" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1787775&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596020169" alt="Riemann" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1787775)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/riemann" >Riemann</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4558017&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596020169" alt="Grigori Karpin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4558017)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" >Grigori Karpin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/el-mickro-el-mackro" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5838281&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596020169" alt="el_mickro-EL_MACKRO" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5838281)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/el-mickro-el-mackro" >el_mickro-EL_MACKRO</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedagon" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5903100&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596020169" alt="Pedagon" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5903100)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedagon" >Pedagon</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ocuin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6104981&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596020169" alt="OCuin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6104981)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ocuin" >OCuin</a></span>'s for feedback during the drafting stage.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Credits</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Credits</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <ul> <li>Quote above is from <em>Alice's Adventures in Wonderland</em> by Lewis Carroll.</li> <li>Sections of FailCon's description were adapted from FailCon's <a href="http://thefailcon.com/about.html">website</a>.</li> <li>Sections of critic reviews were adapted from articles from <a href="https://www.indiewire.com/2019/03/losers-netflix-review-documentary-series-sports-1202047856/">Indiewire</a>, <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2019/mar/01/winners-are-boring-the-genius-netflix-doc-that-celebrates-losers">The Guardian</a> and <a href="https://decider.com/2019/03/04/losers-netflix-stream-it-or-skip-it/">Decider</a>.</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Image&nbsp;Sources</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascrip